### 1. FETCH DATA
POST http://localhost:8080/api/search-bid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dateFrom": "2025-08-01",
  "dateTo": "2026-01-01"
}

### 2. MONITORING: VIEW ALL COLLECTED DATA
GET http://localhost:8080/api/search-bid/all
Accept: application/json

### 3. EXECUTE AI MATCHING (Trigger Python)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matching/run
Accept: application/json

### 4. MONITORING: VIEW REGISTERED USERS
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Accept: application/json

### 5. USER MANAGEMENT: ADD A THIRD USER MANUALLY
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Andreas Tech",
  "age": 38,
  "profession": "Software Engineer",
  "preferredCostMin": 5000,
  "preferredCostMax": 50000,
  "nutsCode": "EL30",
  "cpvCode": "72000000",
  "interests": [
    {"name": "Digital Transformation"},
    {"name": "IoT Solutions"}
  ]
}